HEADWORD: militarized
<hw>militarized</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Equipped with
weapons; armed; -- used of persons, regions, or the military. Contrasted
to <ant>unarmed</ant> and <contr>demilitarized</contr>; <as>as, if
that's a demilitarized zone, I wonder what a <ex>militarized</ex> zone
would look like</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
